findings.description: The contract implements a simple permission check for Aragon OSx. It correctly aggregates liquid token balances and locked balances from a trusted LockManager to compare against a minimum threshold defined in the plugin.
findings.reasoning: This is a general description of the contract's functionality and does not identify any specific vulnerability. It is informational and not security-relevant.
